prompts.frontCover:
A minimalist birthday card front cover for Lao Lao from Jordan. In the center, a cartoon illustration of Lao Lao as a queen, an East Asian woman in her early 20s with long dark hair and thin-rimmed glasses, wearing a royal gown and a crown, sitting on a simple golden throne. She is smiling happily while playfully bonking a jester on the head with a scepter. The jester is Jordan, a Southeast Asian/East Asian man in his early 20s with short black hair and a big joyful smile, wearing a colorful jester hat and outfit. A simple banner above them reads "Another Year of Ruling". In the center, the text "Happy Birthday" is written in beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The style is flat 2D vector art with clean lines, simple shapes, and plenty of white space, capturing the exact smiling expressions from the reference photo. --ar 5:7 --style raw --s 150 --v 6.0 --seed 93262a45-da88-41fd-9362-ab1a94900246

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
